msgid "What's happening?"
msgstr "何？"

msgid "What in the world happened here...?"
msgstr "いったい何があったの……？"

msgid "It's too large to fit in there."
msgstr "大きすぎてここには入らない。"

msgid "Some pieces of old wood."
msgstr "古びた板切れ。"

msgid "They're too old to be useful."
msgstr "古すぎて使えそうにない。"

msgid "The floor in the shrine is unstable."
msgstr "社の床は不安定だ。"

msgid "There's a note here. It says:"
msgstr "メモがある。"

msgid "\"The pipes get clogged sometimes."
msgstr "「時々パイプが詰まることがあります。"

msgid "If that happens, just add:"
msgstr "その場合、以下のものを加えてください。"

msgid "-Some pink petals"
msgstr "・桃色の花びら数枚"

msgid "-Some purple petals"
msgstr "・紫色の花びら数枚"

msgid "-Some white petals"
msgstr "・白い花びら数枚"

msgid "-A bit of black algae"
msgstr "・黒い藻 少量"

msgid "-A bit of green algae"
msgstr "・緑の藻 少量"

msgid "-A bit of blue algae"
msgstr "・青い藻 少量"

msgid "And that's it. Make sure you get the colors right, the little keeper is delicate.\""
msgstr "以上。色を間違えないように気をつけてください、小さな番人は繊細です。」"

msgid "A shrine of some sorts."
msgstr "何かの祭壇。"

msgid "There's a bowl with a goldfish in it."
msgstr "金魚の入った鉢がある。"

msgid "Take the fish?"
msgstr "金魚を取る？"

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "取る"

msgid "No"
msgstr "取らない"

msgid "A window with a view of the water."
msgstr "水面が眺められる窓。"
